g\" src=\"https://f.hdh.im/image_20180704_1d6f068ec3d3f.png!hdnr\" title=\"image_20180704_1d6f068ec3d3f.png\" alt=\"1.png\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">会议背景</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 29px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">2018</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">年</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">4</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">月</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">19</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">日，以</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">“</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">颠覆到合作，金融科技重塑金融新生态</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">”</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">为主题的</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">“</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">第七届中国金融科技峰会</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">”</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">在上海扬子江万丽大酒店隆重召开。本次峰会为期两天，由</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">“PWC|</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">聚想会</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">”</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">主办，以</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">“</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">新</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">”</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">为核心导向，以行业政策解读、市场热点分析、应用案例分享、领袖企业表彰等形式，通过国内外顶尖专家，及业内领军金融科技企业高层等专业人士之口，展现行业最前沿的思想、最具特色的案例，帮助广大金融科技企业以及业内外人士解读行业热点与焦点的同时，找到痛点的解决方案。第七届的成功举办受到业内一致好评。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 29px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">第八届中国金融科技峰会在第七届的基础上总结经验以及客户意见，为了更好地打造金融科技行业的交流平台，将于</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">2018</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">年</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">10</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">月</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">25-26</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">日在北京举行。以</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">““</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">合规</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">”&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">让金融科技稳健前行</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">”</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">为主题，将聚集国内外超过</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">50+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">来自政府，监管层，行业协会，业内专家，企业领袖作相关主题报告，</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">100+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">媒体，</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">400+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">企业，</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">1000+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">参会嘉宾共同就金融机构怎么在合规前提下适度创新？监管如何在培育创新的同时有效规范？金融科技未来会有怎样的发展趋势？科技引领金融的创新发展等话题进行深入探讨。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">部分出席及拟邀嘉宾</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 29px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">吴晓灵，清华大学五道口金融学院理事长，院长</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 29px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">孙国峰，中国人民银行金融研究所所长</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 29px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">陈德霖，香港金融管理局总裁</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 29px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">伍旭川中国人民银行金融研究所互联网金融研究中心秘书长</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 29px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\">李德，中国人民银行参事，中国人民银行研究局原副局长</span></p><p st